Package suncertify.business

This package, and its sub-packages, make up the services layer of application which is responsible for parsing and passing data between the persistence and presentation layer of the application.

Package suncertify.business Description

This package, and its sub-packages, make up the services layer of application which is responsible for parsing and passing data between the persistence and presentation layer of the application. This package in particular contains a default implementation of the services layer's business methods, which is used when running the application in Non-Networked Mode.
